news.title: Graft in PMAY exposed at Jhalawar: Probe
news.para: ​The accused employment assistant was produced before an ACB court on Tuesday that ordered to send him to judicial custody.

news.title: Chennai development body demolishes part of building for setback violations
news.para: According to CMDA officials, the action was taken based on the Madras High Court directive. "There was a litigation and directions were given to the CMDA to remove the portions that were in violation," said an official.

news.title: Kirron Kher's demand to regularise units outside 'lal dora' rejected by Chandigarh admin
news.para: Kher demanded a one-time settlement scheme for regularisation, and a halt to the anti-encroachment drive initiated by the UT against such constructions across the city villages.
